540
00:27:47,068 --> 00:27:48,758
Yeah, I can see that.

541
00:27:48,827 --> 00:27:51,000
[Marty]
It's her nightly routine.

542
00:27:51,068 --> 00:27:52,275
What's wrong with her?

543
00:27:52,344 --> 00:27:53,413
[Marty] I don't know.

544
00:27:53,482 --> 00:27:55,000
She snapped.

545
00:27:55,068 --> 00:27:57,172
Stopped talking
a couple of weeks ago.

546
00:27:57,241 --> 00:28:00,103
