553
00:28:15,586 --> 00:28:17,620
[Nurse] You've got to modify
your behavior.

554
00:28:33,965 --> 00:28:37,310
Are we getting a grip on
not giving our food away?

555
00:28:37,379 --> 00:28:38,827
I told you I didn't
give my food away.

556
00:28:38,896 --> 00:28:43,103
I said, are we getting a grip
on not giving our food away?

557
