The usual.

567
00:29:16,137 --> 00:29:17,689
fought with my mom a lot.

568
00:29:17,758 --> 00:29:19,655
I wasn't crazy or anything,

569
00:29:19,724 --> 00:29:22,586
although I'm not
so sure anymore.

570
00:29:22,655 --> 00:29:24,206
But I'm out of this place.

571
00:29:26,689 --> 00:29:28,551
