Every time I get a chance,
I loosen one of the screws.

575
00:29:35,379 --> 00:29:38,689
Couple of more days
and I'm mystery.

576
00:29:38,758 --> 00:29:41,413
[Nurse] Up. Face the wall.

577
00:29:41,482 --> 00:29:43,793
What, you think you're special?

578
00:29:43,862 --> 00:29:45,896
Come on, face the wall.

579
00:29:48,172 --> 00:29:50,448
[Rachel]
And after that, I don't know.

580
00:29:50,517 --> 00:29:53,172
I just started throwing
up after every meal

