613
00:31:03,655 --> 00:31:05,482
Now you?

614
00:31:05,551 --> 00:31:07,310
I don't have to
take this crap.

615
00:31:07,379 --> 00:31:09,241
[Security] Where do you
think you're going?

616
00:31:09,310 --> 00:31:10,620
I'm going to see Dr Winslow.

617
00:31:10,689 --> 00:31:12,068
Nobody sees Dr. Winslow.

618
00:31:12,137 --> 00:31:13,413
Believe me, if he
has to come in here,

619
00:31:13,482 --> 00:31:14,620
