its against the law.

621
00:31:16,551 --> 00:31:17,793
Not if you're under 18,

622
00:31:17,862 --> 00:31:19,655
but hey, if you want
to call a lawyer.

623
00:31:19,724 --> 00:31:20,931
Then take me to a phone.

624
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:23,793
Sorry, only level two and up
can use the phone.

625
00:31:30,137 --> 00:31:32,137
[Laura yelling]
No! Let me go!

626
00:31:33,965 --> 00:31:35,103
No!

627
00:31:35,172 --> 00:31:37,482
Get off me.

628
00:31:37,551 --> 00:31:38,758
No...

629
00:31:38,827 --> 00:31:40,413
If you settle down, I
won't have to sedate you,

630
00:31:40,482 --> 00:31:41,137
now its your choice.

631
00:31:41,206 --> 00:31:43,275
Go to hell!

632
00:31:43,344 --> 00:31:45,379
Get off me.
No...

633
00:31:45,448 --> 00:31:48,482
[whimpering]

634
00:31:48,551 --> 00:31:50,517
[faintly] No...

635
00:31:50,586 --> 00:31:52,655
[whimpers fade]

636
00:31:58,068 --> 00:32:01,620
[defiant music]

637
00:32:23,379 --> 00:32:25,827
[chatter]

638
00:32:33,586 --> 00:32:36,241
[whispering]
I wanna escape with you.

639
00:32:36,310 --> 00:32:39,034
Why would I let you do that?

640
00:32:39,103 --> 00:32:41,793
Because with the two
of us loosening screws,

641
00:32:41,862 --> 00:32:44,206
it'll come off faster.

642
00:32:44,275 --> 00:32:45,931
All right, but you
gotta be careful.

643
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:49,172
They've got these security
cameras everywhere.

644
00:32:49,241 --> 00:32:51,344
What the hell are
you looking at?

645
00:32:54,344 --> 00:32:55,620
You gotta figure out a way

646
00:32:55,689 --> 00:32:57,517
to get yourself into the main
room when nobody's there.

647
00:32:57,586 --> 00:32:58,758
Best way is to get
yourself in trouble

648
00:32:58,827 --> 00:33:00,379
so you get put on deep clean.

649
00:33:01,931 --> 00:33:04,620
How do I get
myself in trouble?

650
00:33:04,689 --> 00:33:06,586
[chuckles]

651
00:33:19,551 --> 00:33:21,206
[door opens]

652
00:33:23,137 --> 00:33:26,206
You better get a grip on
not sleeping in the hall.

653
00:33:29,482 --> 00:33:31,931
Are you gonna answer me, huh?

654
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:34,000
Or are you gonna play
your usual games?

655
00:33:35,655 --> 00:33:36,965
[whimpering and laughing]

656
00:33:37,034 --> 00:33:39,206
Answer me.

657
00:33:39,275 --> 00:33:40,068
Hey, leave her alone.

658
00:33:40,137 --> 00:33:41,517
She's not gonna hurt anybody.

659
00:33:41,586 --> 00:33:43,517
You just got yourself
two days in deep clean.

660
00:33:43,586 --> 00:33:46,517
[whimpering and laughing]

661
00:33:46,586 --> 00:33:48,655
Are you gonna answer me?

662
00:33:48,724 --> 00:33:52,413
[whimpering]

663
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:56,827
Get up.

664
00:33:56,896 --> 00:33:58,655
-[Naomi whimpers]
-[Nurse shushing]

665
00:33:58,724 --> 00:34:00,896
Come on.

666
00:34:00,965 --> 00:34:02,275
[Naomi whimpers louder]

667
00:34:02,344 --> 00:34:04,068
[Nurse] Show's over.

668
00:34:04,137 --> 00:34:05,551
Everybody get back to your room.

669
00:34:05,620 --> 00:34:06,448
Come on.

670
00:34:11,034 --> 00:34:12,517
[Naomi whimpers]

671
00:34:24,344 --> 00:34:26,724
I want you to clean
the entire floor.

672
00:34:37,275 --> 00:34:42,103
[dramatic music]

673
00:35:22,172 --> 00:35:24,413
[Security man] Make sure it's
done right or you doing it over.

674
00:35:34,655 --> 00:35:37,034
[kung-fu screams]

675
00:35:37,103 --> 00:35:39,000
Oh man...

676
00:35:39,068 --> 00:35:42,103
I love to give that cheesy weesy
a kung-fu action.

677
00:35:44,965 --> 00:35:46,000
[chuckles]

678
00:35:47,655 --> 00:35:48,758
So...

679
00:35:50,551 --> 00:35:53,172
you keeping it
together alright?

680
00:35:53,241 --> 00:35:54,413
Barely.

681
00:35:57,344 --> 00:35:58,931
You'll get the hang
of it. Don't worry.

682
00:36:03,965 --> 00:36:05,000
-[Laura] What'd you do?
-[Marty shushing]

683
00:36:08,965 --> 00:36:11,172
What's the big deal about
talking in this place?

684
00:36:13,103 --> 00:36:15,310
