to make friends.

685
00:36:15,379 --> 00:36:17,275
They want you to
rat on each other.

686
00:36:17,344 --> 00:36:19,241
That's how you get points.

687
00:36:19,310 --> 00:36:22,586
So that's total sex
paranoid in this place.

688
00:36:22,655 --> 00:36:23,758
Like if you're
talking with someone,

689
00:36:23,827 --> 00:36:25,896
they think you're having sex.

690
00:36:25,965 --> 00:36:27,896
Yeah right, that
should be so lucky.

691
00:36:27,965 --> 00:36:29,000
[chuckles]

692
00:36:36,068 --> 00:36:37,758
What did you do
to get deep clean?

693
00:36:39,689 --> 00:36:41,896
Eh...

694
00:36:41,965 --> 00:36:42,896
I don't know.

695
00:36:42,965 --> 00:36:44,724
I found some stupid white out

696
00:36:44,793 --> 00:36:46,689
