counselors desks.

697
00:36:48,448 --> 00:36:49,793
What, were you
like sniffing it?

698
00:36:52,172 --> 00:36:53,413
Sniffing it?

699
00:36:53,482 --> 00:36:55,517
No, I was, eh--

700
00:36:55,586 --> 00:36:58,931
I was gonna use it to paint
this little house I built.

701
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,551
What little house?

702
00:37:05,241 --> 00:37:06,862
This house is made
up of an old meal box,

703
00:37:06,931 --> 00:37:08,448
I stole it from the kitchen.

704
00:37:12,931 --> 00:37:14,896
It's for Phoebe here.

705
00:37:14,965 --> 00:37:16,172
[smiles]

706
00:37:16,241 --> 00:37:17,206
Hey.

707
00:37:17,275 --> 00:37:19,034
Hi.

708
00:37:19,103 --> 00:37:20,862
Oh look, she's so cute.

709
00:37:20,931 --> 00:37:22,586
