00:38:07,793 --> 00:38:09,689
We wouldn't have to
talk or anything.

723
00:38:09,758 --> 00:38:12,275
We just know that we were there.

724
00:38:12,344 --> 00:38:14,344
You know like...

725
00:38:14,413 --> 00:38:16,137
friends do...

726
00:38:16,206 --> 00:38:17,965
and like eh...

727
00:38:18,034 --> 00:38:19,724
pen-pals or something,

728
00:38:19,793 --> 00:38:21,827
separated by thousands of miles.

729
00:38:23,793 --> 00:38:26,103
