730
00:38:26,172 --> 00:38:28,068
Yeah. I'd like
to be your friend.

731
00:38:28,137 --> 00:38:32,137
[soft music]

732
00:38:47,206 --> 00:38:49,172
Wow.

733
00:38:49,241 --> 00:38:50,413
Hardly recognize a meal

734
00:38:50,482 --> 00:38:52,137
