a Styrofoam container.

735
00:38:52,206 --> 00:38:53,689
I guess it has been a while
since we showed

736
00:38:53,758 --> 00:38:54,827
at the dinner table together.

737
00:38:57,689 --> 00:39:01,000
It's so hard for me to get
out of the office before seven,

738
00:39:01,068 --> 00:39:02,206
