743
00:39:22,689 --> 00:39:24,482
I miss the kids.

744
00:39:24,551 --> 00:39:26,344
Well... I mean.

745
00:39:32,551 --> 00:39:33,793
I tried to call Laura today.

746
00:39:35,862 --> 00:39:37,862
Robert, you shouldn't
have done that.

747
00:39:37,931 --> 00:39:38,931
You know what they said?

748
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:40,068
She needs to be
separated from us.

749
00:39:40,137 --> 00:39:41,620
I know, I couldn't help it.

750
00:39:41,689 --> 00:39:42,896
They said she was fine

751
00:39:42,965 --> 00:39:44,137
