come to the phone, so--

752
00:39:47,103 --> 00:39:49,000
I just hope she's really okay.

753
00:39:52,620 --> 00:39:54,965
Don't do this to
yourself Robert.

754
00:39:55,034 --> 00:39:57,103
We need to give this a chance.

755
00:39:57,172 --> 00:39:59,896
