756
00:39:59,965 --> 00:40:02,000
It's only 11 more days.

757
00:40:03,758 --> 00:40:05,586
Yeah...

758
00:40:05,655 --> 00:40:07,448
But who's counting, huh?

759
00:40:13,758 --> 00:40:17,000
[radio chatter]

760
00:40:20,034 --> 00:40:20,896
