771
00:40:55,655 --> 00:40:58,344
Maybe he likes you.

772
00:40:58,413 --> 00:41:01,344
I don't think so, it's
different than that.

773
00:41:01,413 --> 00:41:02,551
I wouldn't trust him.

774
00:41:02,620 --> 00:41:04,172
As far as I could drop,
kick a range Rover.

775
00:41:06,068 --> 00:41:08,206
