No, I really should go.

1491
01:22:02,896 --> 01:22:03,862
I'll call you again.

1492
01:22:03,931 --> 01:22:04,758
Laura.

1493
01:22:04,827 --> 01:22:05,931
Okay.

1494
01:22:08,241 --> 01:22:11,068
Gladys, call the
district attorney's office.

1495
01:22:11,137 --> 01:22:12,413
